Highly extendable soundboard.
-	Create folders numbered 0-(n-1) (where n is the constant 
	NUM_COL) in the directory containing the executable

-	Add a file to each name n.txt

-	Add the number of buttons you want for the colum to n.txt (ONLY 
	ADD THIS, NOTHING ELSE)

-	Add wave files and button images numbered from 0 to what you put 
	in n.txt (e.g for the first button in the first folder, you 
	add 0.png and 0.wav to ~/projectDir/0/)

-	Optionally change the header and background image
